00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:48,590
You know him well.

375
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:49,960
He doesn't say anything.

376
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:53,200
He's awake.

377
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,880
