00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:15,310
How is Zhang Qi's illness?

408
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:17,880
He made a fast training,

409
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,350
plus the fresh soldiers of our squadron,

